28
00:09:19,038 --> 00:09:29,888
Now I plant it in a pot so the orchid can grow in an outside environment.

29
00:09:36,192 --> 00:09:45,884
I used aquaponic plastic beads and terracotta spread underneath.

30
00:09:45,884 --> 00:09:55,882
and spread moss on the surface to help retain moisture better.

